small businesses from the Shoko Chukin Bank in Tokyo.  NOTE: Survey sample comprises about 900 small and medium-sized businesses.
NOTE1: 3 month moving averages do not include forecasts.
NOTE2: The year on year percentage change in the Construction and Real estate
sectors are more volatile than the other sectors. 
